Subject: Re: [T2] Upper bunk bed for sportsmobile conversion

Didn't the donor give you the roof hinges and brackets with the top?
The easiest way would be to set the top on the roof and mark where the
mounting brackets fall. I wouldn't build the bed until you see where
the mounts are.

